Blessed with an infectious effervescence this woman grabs your attention and demands admiration. An eternal optimist with an indescribable zest for life she is the unsung hero in this big bad world. Even when she faces hardships - she gets up dusts herself off sprays on a bit of Diesel Fuel for Life and moves on with a smile. Created by the esteemed noses of Annick Menardo Thierry Wasser and Jacques Cavallier this enlivening Eau De Parfum is made for the vibrant house of Diesel.

An aromatic infusion that sends a shock through your being right from the first whiff. Each ingredient triggers a long forgotten memory that has taught her something very valuable. The tart hints of blackcurrant reminds her of seemingly sweet endeavours that ended in a bitter note. Green and minty hints of patchouli makes her think of the time she learnt it was wiser to stay cool and composed instead of having an outburst. Exotic and heady notes of jasmine make her think of her mother and the comforting words she gave about going after her dreams. A glorious luxury perfume she can wear this at any time she wants to energise her tired mind and soul. A radiant elixir this fragrance is poured into a beautiful vial that resembles the shape of a single drop. Glowing a regal shade of gold with a shining gold stopper this perfume shifts your life into top gear.

Diesel Loverdose Eau de Parfum - 75 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.3600

While your head tells you what is wise her aura envelopes you in a delightful quicksand of emotions and tells you otherwise. Irresistible is her middle name she revels in the effect she can have when she saunters into the room causing every face to whip around and every heart to do a tiny skip. Diesel Loverdose luxury fragrance makes it crystal clear - she fills your senses to the hilt while keeping a cool maddening distance.

Diesel scores an edge with the sheer effect of the fragrance - creating an illusion of innocence but all through maintaining surprising assertiveness. The enchanting Eau de Parfum spices up your simple life with citrusy opening notes of mandarin orange and star anise. Heart notes of jasmine gardenia and licorice scramble your thought process while they slowly dissipate to give way to a cozy comforting vanilla and amber. She’s like a firework that leaves glowing embers behind mild yet possibly explosive.

The name itself is a play on words overdose of love or a dose of the lover. The theme is taken to another level with the bottle which is designed in the shape of a heart-shaped diamond - you can never decide if she has the warmth of a heart or the undying strength of a diamond. Accentuated with vibrant shades of purple her memories last long after she has waltzed gracefully out of your life.
